snippet.title: Hello Kitty Food Town - Fulfill Your Restaurant Dreams with Hello Kitty!
snippet.description:
Subscribe to the channel: https://bit.ly/2ZgNWyh

Hello Kitty Food Town By Sanrio Digital
Play the game: 
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sd.google.helloKittyFoodTown&hl=None

Welcome to Hello Kitty Food Town! Fulfill your restaurant dreams with Hello Kitty, Keroppi and all their friends! Challenge culinary standards with innovative recipes and keep customers satisfied with your fingerlicking good food! 

Hello Kitty wishes to spread love and joy with food and has decided to help you run the day-to-day operations of your little restaurant. Decorate your own Food Town from a broad selection of Hello Kitty-themed furniture, wallpapers, floor tiles, and decors to invite more customers! Serve yummy meals like Little Red Cakes, Mochi, Strawberry Bows, and learn more delectable recipes as you level up! But before anything else, you'll have to grow your very own farm to make sure your ingredients are always fresh! 

Hello Kitty Nail Salon: http://bit.ly/2KwZjws

More Games: https://www.babygames.com/

#BabyGamesVideos #HelloKittyFoodTown #HelloKitty #Game #ForKids
